    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Buildings having between four or five and nine or ten stories and equipped with elevators; generally applied to commercial buildings and apartment houses.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
